    &quot;&quot;&quot;
)

tasks.create(&quot;MyTask&quot;) {
    println(
        &quot;&quot;&quot;
        I am defined in a task and
        run at the configration phase of build process&quot;&quot;&quot;
    )
    doLast {
        // ...
    }
}
```

See [this answer](https://stackoverflow.com/a/52139585/8583692) and [this answer](https://stackoverflow.com/a/60252724/8583692) for how to import a function from another script in Kotlin DSL.


